    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund Medicinal Reviews for Patients Prescribed Highly Addictive Drugs",
        "additional_details": "Unchecked prescriptions for addictive drugs may fuel a public health crisis. I believe that mandatory reviews would protect patients, reduce addiction cases, and show the Government\u2019s commitment to safer, more responsible healthcare.",
        "background": "We ask Government to fund medicinal reviews for patients prescribed addictive drugs, ensuring regular assessments, informed consent, and accountability. Reviews would explore alternative treatments and monitor patient well-being to prevent dependency and foster safer prescribing practices.",
